    <div style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS'; border:groove; background-color:blanchedalmond;">
    <h2 style="background-color:cornflowerblue;">Document Required for Driving licence</h2>
        <p>To ensure that there is no delay in the application process, the documents that are to be submitted have to be valid and correct.
&nbsp&nbsp The list of documents required for driving licence are:</p>

&nbsp&nbsp<b style="background-color:lightpink;">Age Proof (any one of the below given documents)</b>
        <br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Birth Certificate<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp PanCard<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Passport<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp 10th Class mark sheet<br />
&nbsp&nbsp;&nbsp; Transfer certificate from any school for any class with date of birth printed on it<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<h4 style="background-color:cornflowerblue;">Proof of Address required for DL:</h4>
        <p><b style="background-color:lightpink;">Permanent</b> Proof of address (any one from the following):</p>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Passport<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Aadhaar Card<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Self-owned house agreement<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Electricity bill (issued in applicants name)<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp LIC bond<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Voters ID Card<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp Ration card<br />
        <p><b style="background-color:lightpink;" >Current</b> Proof of address (any one from the following):</p>
           
                &nbsp&nbsp Rental agreement and electricity bill<br />
               &nbsp&nbsp  Rental agreement and LPG bill<br />
            
     
        <h4 style="background-color:cornflowerblue;"><b>Other Requirements for Driving Licence:</b></h4>

&nbsp Duly filled application form (to get the application form for driving licence, visit the nearest RTO or download it from the online portal for your state)<br />
&nbsp&nbsp 6 passport sized photographs (when applying for Learners Licence)<br />
&nbsp&nbsp 1 passport sized photograph (when applying for driving licence)<br />
&nbsp&nbsp Application Fees<br />
&nbsp&nbsp If you are staying in other cities, as current address proof, you can present the rental agreement with one recent utility bill copy which can be gas bill or electric bill<br />
&nbsp&nbsp Medical Certificate - Form 1 A and 1 which is to be issued by a certified Government doctor<br />
&nbsp&nbsp For all applicants over the age of 40 years, a Medical certificate is mandatory.<br />
